            <thetext>Steps to reproduce:

1) Open the &quot;TabView&quot; demo at the demobrowser
2) Choose the second tab view (the one with 20 tabs)
3) Scroll to the right to the last tab
4) Close all visible tabs from right to left

In Firefox you end up with an empty space because every tab is closed and the TabView bar does not scroll when closing the tabs.
I only saw this issue at Firefox 3 all the others (IE, Safari and Opera) are not affected.</thetext>
